Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.75,0:21:50.25,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}INSIDE  IDENTITY
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.25,0:21:53.05,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我的栖身之地在哪儿？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:05.69,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}误解令人感到害羞什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.77,0:22:08.27,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}率真令人难以忍受什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.40,0:22:10.61,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}无论他人怎么说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.61,0:22:13.49,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我也不知到底「正确」为何物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.53,0:22:16.11,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}强迫自己去习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.32,0:22:18.70,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一成不变的日常
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:21.45,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}将沉沦的种种个性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.54,0:22:23.66,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}啃食饮尽  唾弃嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.70,0:22:28.29,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}希望你能理解这样的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.38,0:22:33.63,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}欲言又止
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:38.59,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}连思考「为什么谁人都无法理解我」
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.72,0:22:43.68,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}都已成为一种奢侈了吗？了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:48.98,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}多愁善感的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.06,0:22:51.69,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}释放出过多的热量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.77,0:22:54.11,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}把我晒得快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.23,0:22:59.20,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}按耐不住呐喊的冲动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:05.20,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不顾一切地渴求IDENTITY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.20,0:23:07.66,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}INSIDE  MY  FEELING
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.75,0:23:10.25,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}INSIDE  MY  JUSTICE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:12.79,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}千万别妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.88,0:23:14.84,EDlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}我的栖身之地在哪儿？
